      "text": "\n[Spanish involvement in the tribal dissidence in northern Morocco may cause Rabat to renew pressure for the evacuations of the 10,000 Spanish troops remaining in Morocco. Rabat has repeatedly protested Spanish complicity.]\n\n[Moroccan Vice Premier Bouabd, who with other officials recently inspected military activities in northern Morocco, stated] the Royal Army has proof that Spain has supplied arms and money to the Beni Ouraghel tribe. Bouabd also claimed he has discovered a definite separatist movement in the Rif and that the Beni Ouraghel--the tribe of Rifian warrior Abd-el-Krim who rebelled against Spain in the '1920s'--apparently are determined to set up a Rif republic.",
