      "text": "[Moroccan Vice Premier Bouabd, who with other officials recently inspected military activities in northern Morocco, stated] the Royal Army has proof that Spain has supplied arms and money to the Beni Ouraghel tribe. Bouabd also claimed he has discovered a definite separatist movement in the Rif and that the Beni Ouraghel--the tribe of Rifian warrior Abd-el-Krim who rebelled against Spain in the '1920s'--apparently are determined to set up a Rif republic.",
      "char_len": 458,
      "line_kind": "text_line",
      "line_box_xyxy": [
        6,
        120,
        515,
        130
      ]
    },
    {
